  "detailed_description": "Under the siege of a large number of zombies for 20 minutes.<br><br>You can choose a different career start.<br>After entering the game, a large number of zombies will besiege you.<br>You need to destroy them quickly and pick up the experience ball.<br>Reasonably select active skills or passive skills when upgrading.<br>There are currently 12 active skills.<br>12 passive skills.<br>After the active skill reaches the full level. You can evolve active skills by defeating the boss and dropping props.<br>Active skills will be more powerful after evolution.<br>Holding out for 20 minutes in front of hordes of zombies is victory.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933800/extras/60fbc800fb6e4690650ca2d8e8db5859.poster.avif?t=1648218857\" width=534 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933800/extras/60fbc800fb6e4690650ca2d8e8db5859.webm?t=1648218857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933800/extras/60fbc800fb6e4690650ca2d8e8db5859.mp4?t=1648218857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Under the siege of a large number of zombies for 20 minutes.<br><br>You can choose a different career start.<br>After entering the game, a large number of zombies will besiege you.<br>You need to destroy them quickly and pick up the experience ball.<br>Reasonably select active skills or passive skills when upgrading.<br>There are currently 12 active skills.<br>12 passive skills.<br>After the active skill reaches the full level. You can evolve active skills by defeating the boss and dropping props.<br>Active skills will be more powerful after evolution.<br>Holding out for 20 minutes in front of hordes of zombies is victory.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933800/extras/60fbc800fb6e4690650ca2d8e8db5859.poster.avif?t=1648218857\" width=534 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933800/extras/60fbc800fb6e4690650ca2d8e8db5859.webm?t=1648218857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933800/extras/60fbc800fb6e4690650ca2d8e8db5859.mp4?t=1648218857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
